<TEXT>
here are key dates in the life of emperor hirohito 
the 124th occupant of japans chrysanthemum throne 
1901 april 29 born in tokyo 
1916 becomes crown prince 
1921 tours united kingdom france the netherlands belgium and 
italy 
1924 marries princess nagako 
1926 becomes emperor following the death of his father emperor 
taisho 
1928 formally installed as emperor 
1933 first son and current crown prince akihito born 
1945 aug 15 announces by radio japans defeat in world war ii 
1946 jan 1 renounces his divinity 
1971 becomes first reigning japanese emperor to travel abroad 
visiting belgium the united kingdom west germany and four other 
european nations 
1975 with the empress visits the united states 
1989 jan 7 dies of cancer 
</TEXT>
