<TEXT>
a senior member of afghanistans 
sovietstyle ruling party said today that deposed king zahir shah 
could play a role in ending the afghan war but president najib would 
not resign 
najmuddin kawyani one of 14 politburo members of the peoples 
democratic party of afghanistan accused antigovernment guerrillas 
of blocking efforts to form a broadbased government 
