japans stock markets closed but banks and many shops remained open 
some clerks wore black ribbons to signify mourning but prepared 
by the monarchs long illness people generally reacted calmly 
in western japan however an 87yearold man hanged himself 
today leaving a note that said in part i want to follow the 
