public organizations like the culture fund will be submitted to the 
organizations congresses and conferences in march for a vote in 
addition 1500 deputies will be elected to represent territorial 
divisions and the 15 constituent soviet republics 
the culture fund is an umbrella group for the arts that tries to 
involve more soviets in cultural pursuits provide financial support 
and help young artists gain public recognition 
mrs gorbachev a former philosophy teacher arouses strong 
passions among soviets some admire what they view as her sense of 
style while others condemn her for extravagant taste in clothes and 
